;Expand %vars% in string, converting %% (double percent sequences) to %
; tries to find var name in:
; 1. substVars:
;   - { varname: value             ; direct substitution
;   - , varname: function_object } ; substitutes to return value of the function
; 2. EnvVars
; 3. script variables
; 4. substVars[""]
